==English==

===Etymology===
Originated as slang in the U.S. Army in the Second World War. The first word is sometimes [[bowdlerize|Bowdlerized]] as ''Fouled''. Also used in the movie [[Saving Private Ryan]]

==={{acronym}}===
'''fubar''' or '''FUBAR'''
# [[Fucked]] Up Beyond All Recognition (or Repair), or Fouled Up Beyond All Recognition.

